- Design and construct precast concrete box culverts according to Section 578.
- Excavate and backfill according to Section 209.
- For precast concrete box culverts, submit design drawings and details with supporting calculations according to Subsection 104.06.
- Construct precast concrete box culverts according to Section 578.[[SRC_1]]

